  <b>1.1.3</b>
  <ul>
    <li>Undo checkpoints - press Menu and select "Set checkpoint" while in game. You can later
    return to this checkpoint by selecting "Undo to checkpoint" (issue #109, thanks to
    thexbin).</li>
    <li>Some users report problems with install / update, this update hopefully fixes that.</li>
    <li>Fixes bug with undo when under certain circumstances undo information is lost (issue
    #86).</li>
  </ul>
  <b>1.1.2</b>
  <ul>
    <li>Manual import of puzzles from SD card - just press Menu and select Import (thanks to dracul
    for this).</li>
    <li>OpenSudoku is now installed on SD card by default.</li>
  </ul>
